<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About • Spenza</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
            font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
        }

        body{
            background:#0f0f10;
            color:#fff;
            line-height:1.7;
        }

        a{
            text-decoration:none;
            color:inherit;
        }

        nav{
            width:90%;
            max-width:1200px;
            margin:auto;
            padding:25px 0;
            display:flex;
            justify-content:space-between;
            align-items:center;
        }

        .logo{
            font-size:32px;
            font-weight:800;
        }

        .logo span{
            color:#16c05d;
        }

        .back{
            color:#999;
        }

        .container{
            width:90%;
            max-width:1100px;
            margin:auto;
            padding:40px 0 80px;
        }

        h1{
            font-size:54px;
            margin-bottom:20px;
        }

        .hero p{
            color:#b3b3b3;
            max-width:700px;
            font-size:18px;
        }

        section{
            margin-top:70px;
        }

        h2{
            margin-bottom:18px;
            font-size:28px;
        }

        p{
            color:#bdbdbd;
        }

        .grid{
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));
            gap:20px;
            margin-top:25px;
        }

        .card{
            background:#171717;
            border:1px solid #252525;
            padding:25px;
            border-radius:16px;
            transition:.25s;
        }

        .card:hover{
            transform:translateY(-4px);
            border-color:#f5a000;
        }

        .card h3{
            margin-bottom:10px;
        }

        .tech{
            display:flex;
            flex-wrap:wrap;
            gap:12px;
            margin-top:20px;
        }

        .badge{
            background:#171717;
            border:1px solid #2c2c2c;
            padding:10px 18px;
            border-radius:999px;
        }

        .developer{
            background:#171717;
            border:1px solid #252525;
            padding:35px;
            border-radius:18px;
        }

        .links{
            display:flex;
            gap:18px;
            margin-top:18px;
            flex-wrap:wrap;
        }

        .btn{
            padding:12px 20px;
            border-radius:10px;
            background:#f5a000;
            color:#111;
            font-weight:700;
        }

        .btn.secondary{
            background:#222;
            color:#fff;
            border:1px solid #333;
        }

        footer{
            text-align:center;
            color:#7b7b7b;
            padding:50px 0;
            border-top:1px solid #222;
            margin-top:80px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>

    <div class="logo">
        Spen<span>za</span>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="back">← Back Home</a>

</nav>

<div class="container">

    <section class="hero">

        <h1>About Spenza</h1>

        <p>
            Spenza is a modern expense tracking application built to make
            personal finance simple, organized, and accessible.
            Record expenses, monitor spending, and gain insights into your
            financial habits through a clean and intuitive interface.
        </p>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h2>Why Spenza?</h2>

        <p>
            Managing daily expenses shouldn't feel complicated.
            Spenza focuses on speed, simplicity, and clarity so users can
            spend less time organizing finances and more time making informed
            financial decisions.
        </p>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h2>Features</h2>

        <div class="grid">

            <div class="card">
                <h3>💸 Expense Tracking</h3>
                <p>Add, edit and manage daily expenses effortlessly.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>📊 Analytics</h3>
                <p>Visualize your spending with charts and monthly summaries.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>📂 Categories</h3>
                <p>Organize expenses with custom categories.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>📑 Reports</h3>
                <p>Review previous transactions anytime.</p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h2>Built With</h2>

        <div class="tech">

            <div class="badge">Node.js</div>
            <div class="badge">Express.js</div>
            <div class="badge">MongoDB</div>
            <div class="badge">EJS</div>
            <div class="badge">HTML5</div>
            <div class="badge">CSS3</div>
            <div class="badge">JavaScript</div>

        </div>

    </section>

    <section>

        <h2>Developer</h2>

        <div class="developer">

            <h3>Prathmesh Naphade</h3>

            <p>
                Engineering student and Full Stack + AI Developer passionate
                about building practical products that solve real-world
                problems.
            </p>

            <div class="links">

                <a href="https://github.com/PTH-15"
                   target="_blank"
                   class="btn secondary">
                    GitHub
                </a>

                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/prathmesh-naphade/"
                   target="_blank"
                   class="btn">
                    LinkedIn
                </a>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

</div>

<footer>

    <p>Spenza • Version 1.0.0</p>
    <p>Designed & Developed by Prathmesh Naphade</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>